            </div>
            <p><code>spells doctor</code> runs 10 distinct checks — <code>$PATH</code> integration, manifest discovery, extends cycles, wrapper drift, shadowing, placeholder/param consistency, override usage, shell init, state versioning. Plus a versioned binary manifest cache that keeps TAB completion sub-perceptible, <code>extends:</code> inheritance with closer-manifest-wins overrides, and one native Swift binary on disk — no Node, no Python, no <code>node_modules</code>.</p>
            <div class="snippet">
              <span class="snippet__label">terminal</span>
              <pre><code>{`$ spells doctor
  ✓ manifest      spells.yaml + 1 parent (extends chain ok)
  ✓ PATH          ~/.local/bin and ~/.spellbook/bin both reachable
  ✓ shell init    zsh integration loaded (TAB completion live)
  ✓ wrappers      12 wrappers match manifest, 0 drift
  ✓ shadowing     no spell shadows a $PATH binary without override
  ✓ placeholders  every {{name}} resolves to a declared param
  ✓ state         snapshot version 3 (current)
  ⚠ stale cache   1 orphan from /Users/me/old-proj (run \`spells clean --orphans\`)

  → 0 errors, 1 warning`}</code></pre>
